      "bullets": [
        "SpaceX's Starfall program targets rapid, point-to-point global cargo delivery utilizing its Starship heavy-lift orbital launch vehicle architecture.",
        "The initiative positions SpaceX for Department of Defense Rocket Cargo contracts, aiming for under-one-hour orbital transit times globally.",
        "Key engineering hurdles include developing rapid orbital payload deployment systems, thermal protection for cargo, and precise terrestrial landing infrastructure."
